Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.26,0:00:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要保持室内光亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.00,0:00:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还要别太近看电视啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.83,0:00:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又有一名怪人出现唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.67,0:00:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.98,0:00:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这全部都是久留美的力量数据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.18,0:00:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不只瞬间的反应
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.85,0:00:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,破坏力亦是远超我们的想像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.09,0:00:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而资料分析亦明确指出久留美的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.43,0:00:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ANGEL  HEART.改
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.03,0:00:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经完全起动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.36,0:00:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与我们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.03,0:00:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ANGEL  HEART不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.43,0:00:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“改”是必须巫术的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.27,0:00:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才可以完全起动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.80,0:00:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,换言之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.07,0:00:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,世界上真的有巫师的存在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.84,0:00:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，应该是那个叫仲人的少年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.84,0:00:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少年?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.98,0:00:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.15,0:00:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美绝对服从那个少年吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.68,0:02:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.29,0:02:38.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃点吧，慢慢咀嚼唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.93,0:02:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美小姐...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.56,0:02:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.97,0:02:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.94,0:02:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请等等啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.78,0:03:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美小姐，那人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.25,0:03:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.22,0:03:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆，久留美帮你搬唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.62,0:03:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.66,0:03:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，多得你的帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.43,0:03:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好多人唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.33,0:03:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是大都市
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.70,0:04:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，看来太多人了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.70,0:04:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能有什么事发生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.87,0:04:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大尾张烟花大会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.44,0:04:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有烟花大会啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.04,0:04:11.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烟花，烟花，烟花唷!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.38,0:04:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烟花唷!烟花大会的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.72,0:04:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圆形的，花形的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.23,0:04:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮唷!主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.70,0:04:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对，但天上的灿烂的烟花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.14,0:04:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也及不上久留美的美貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.17,0:04:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.34,0:04:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.19,0:04:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今夜将会是一个令人难忘的晚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.86,0:04:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，久留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.56,0:04:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们明天一早便要出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.73,0:05:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚没有时间去看烟花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.40,0:05:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，不行，不行唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.10,0:05:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚一定要去看烟花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.90,0:05:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美小姐，不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.64,0:05:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要听从天城博士的说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.61,0:05:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，但是，但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.48,0:05:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在旅馆里也一定可以看到烟花的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.88,0:05:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和主人一起欣赏吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.85,0:05:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就好唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.82,0:05:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上去旅馆唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.15,0:05:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是那边，是行这边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.56,0:05:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.56,0:05:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,博士，快带路唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.97,0:05:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想在姐姐的怀中...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.68,0:05:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看得好清楚唷，主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.45,0:05:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里一定是名古屋欣赏烟花的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.52,0:05:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最佳位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.02,0:06:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来唷，这边唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.76,0:06:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.50,0:06:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,旅馆的主人真好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.17,0:06:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.28,0:06:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来仲人已经习惯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.32,0:06:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.85,0:06:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他终于明白自己对久留美的责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.59,0:06:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙希，你不去吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.16,0:06:41.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?不...不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.33,0:06:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.60,0:06:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了姐姐吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.54,0:06:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真想博士是一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.31,0:06:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，喂，这是任务啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.24,0:06:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.85,0:07:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也想和那个仲人单独一起吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.58,0:07:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎会...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.75,0:07:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么，这是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.02,0:07:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亲笔写的同人志一美少年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.22,0:07:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要，不要，不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.79,0:07:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仲人纤细的双手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.00,0:07:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就如红叶般随风飘动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.80,0:07:22.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他雪白的牙齿，令我的身体发热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.37,0:07:23.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令人生染上色彩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.07,0:07:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害羞得令人不禁长嗟短叹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.65,0:07:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎说才好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.58,0:07:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种生活...还要到何时?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.19,0:07:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害，好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.43,0:07:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.53,0:07:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.07,0:07:54.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是第一次这么近欣赏烟花的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.90,0:07:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圆形唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.67,0:08:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花形唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.41,0:08:05.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圆形唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.72,0:08:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人也一起叫吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.39,0:08:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始了唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.12,0:08:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.79,0:08:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圆形唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.47,0:08:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.08,0:08:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美小姐...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.95,0:08:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很漂...漂亮呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.05,0:08:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.69,0:08:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真...是不可思议呢...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.46,0:08:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到烟花后才听到声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.00,0:08:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.40,0:09:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美小姐   什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.77,0:09:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们偶然遇上...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.45,0:09:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知什么原因...我们来到这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.35,0:09:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我终于明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.12,0:09:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.79,0:09:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对久留美小姐的责任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.66,0:09:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总而言之...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.67,0:09:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.21,0:09:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.17,0:09:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很...很...很喜欢你唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.44,0:09:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美小姐...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.55,0:09:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.18,0:09:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有点口渴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.65,0:09:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿点饮品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.69,0:09:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美去拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.39,0:09:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人在这里等我唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.65,0:10:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很冰冻的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.48,0:10:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，婶婶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.49,0:10:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.71,0:10:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人...咦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.28,0:10:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人，你在哪里啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.06,0:11:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.03,0:11:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁人叫我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.13,0:11:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听到我的声音吗?久留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.94,0:11:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.04,0:11:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我捉了你的主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.04,0:11:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.68,0:11:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.65,0:11:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.82,0:11:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就来到我身处的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.66,0:11:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.54,0:11:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.37,0:11:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧，久留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.34,0:11:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来到我身处的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.68,0:12:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.65,0:12:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种难忘的夜晚...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.38,0:12:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.05,0:12:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主人...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.79,0:12:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.43,0:12:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.95,0:12:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“二人看烟花唷”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.58,0:14:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集久留美会多了几个朋友唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.18,0:14:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来并不是这么简单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.25,0:14:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不简单的话就简易吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.58,0:14:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.99,0:14:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钢铁天使久留美，第十话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.89,0:14:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我来接你的”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.26,0:14:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不容错过唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.86,0:14:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很开心，很开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.30,0:14:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集久留美会多了几个朋友唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.30,0:14:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美小姐，看来不是这么简单
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.83,0:14:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那即是很沉郁的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.50,0:14:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡说什么啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.50,0:14:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一定是无忧无虑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.81,0:14:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.91,0:14:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是悠闲，不是沉郁，不是无忧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.24,0:14:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那即是郁气吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.11,0:14:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那...那是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.41,0:14:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不畅快的意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.91,0:14:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可没听过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.45,0:14:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钢铁天使久留美，第十话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.18,0:14:50.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我来接你的”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.39,0:14:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不容错过...唷
